summary: Haunted has to be one of my favorite/one of the most relatable songs ever because when my ex broke up with me i knew he was...
body: Haunted has to be one of my favorite/one of the most relatable songs ever because when my ex broke up with me i knew he was falling out of love with me but i didn’t wanna believe it. I spent every second after the breakup wondering where it went wrong and annalyzing every text that was read but wasn’t answered for hours and every cancelled plan. This song was one of the soundtracks to my tears and holds such an important place in my life. So, to the people who got to hear this song live last night, damn you’re lucky!

tags: i wanna send taylor my wedding invite!
I am sending Taylor swift a wedding invitation
summary:
And then, a few months later - I got engaged! 
And now that the wedding is about a year away, I'm totally sending @taylorswift...
body:
About a year ago, I made this post

And then, a few months later - I got engaged!

And now that the wedding is about a year away, I’m totally sending @taylorswift an invitation.

I totally wasn’t kidding! I’m really sending it!

I found the address online and am praying, PRAYING it is still active - last “success” in someone finding out their letter was recieved was Dec 2017. So here it goes! @taylornation

I wrote a letter to go with it, but I could have kept writing for hours…

Anyway, wish me luck!

It would mean a lot if you passed this around to increase my chances of Taylor knowing the invitation is coming 💕
